 Alaskan Husky , Sarabi , was returned to a friend of the musher Laura Allaway , will be reunited with the animal on April 28 when she returns from traveling .
The three-year-old dog was spotted on April 15 near Glenn Highway and then Friday near Reverend Tim Carrick 's team on Monday night .
Sarabi escaped from handlers on March 21 after being dropped by the Iditarod race .